      <title>西班牙与其他欧盟国家一起计划终止黄金签证</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/spain-to-end-golden-visa-program-for-real-estate-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙计划结束针对外国购房者的所谓黄金签证计划，以增加当地人可获得的经济适用住房的数量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/spain-to-end-golden-visa-program-for-real-estate-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 11:55:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>戴蒙将人工智能的变革性影响比作蒸汽机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/dimon-says-ai-could-be-as-transformational-as-the-steam-engine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通公司首席执行官杰米·戴蒙 (Jamie Dimon) 表示，人工智能可能是该银行正在努力解决的最大问题，他将其潜在影响与蒸汽机的潜在影响进行了比较，并表示该技术可以“增强几乎所有工作岗位”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/dimon-says-ai-could-be-as-transformational-as-the-steam-engine</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 10:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
